summary: Fixes the \"Party\" of Elenwens to be better
descriptionHtml:
Fixes the \"Party\" of Elenwens to be better
_____________________________________________
[color=red][b]SPOILERS[/b][/color] 
For those who have completed The Blade\'s Spy mission to infiltrate the Thalmor party, you\'ll know 3 or four people isn\'t really a party, this just adds a few more guests and servants to the party as wel as fixes the thalmor robes in the side room to be hooded. That\'s it so enjoy!
_______________________________________________
